snippet.title: Heart Chain Kitty - Nintendo Switch Trailer
snippet.description:
Heart Chain Kitty arrives on the Nintendo Switch on August 20! A big and colorful 3d platform adventure is waiting. Dive deep into your dreams and save your parents!
https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/heart-chain-kitty-switch/
